	  <h1 class = "pages-title">
	    What is MUN?
	  </h1>
	  <p class = "pages-description">
	    As an organization, we teach members how to emulate the United Nations. Members step in the shoes of foreign diplomats and take on their perspective in order to come up with solutions to complet global problems. At these conferences, student delegates debate current events, give speeches, draft policy resolutions, form political alliances and resolve international conflicts - all from the perspective of their assigned country. In doing so, Model UN brings together curious students with a passion for exploring the world’s most challenging problems.
	  </p>
	  <p class = "pages-description">
	    Model United Nations at UCSD additionally aims to help participants practice public speaking, elevate the depth of research papers, and be a more confident version of themselves. Our dedicated Secretariat believes in training an army of erudites, capable of analyzing and questioning every governmental action and institutional goal. It’s our world; we don’t just live in it.
	  </p>			
